<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Account Activated - EduConnextX</title>
    <style type="text/css">
        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            min-width: 100%;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            font-size: 16px;
            line-height: 1.5;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            color: #333;
        }

        a {
            color: #0070f3;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 26px;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-top: 0;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            color: white;
        }

        p {
            margin: 0 0 20px 0;
            color: #555;
        }

        .email_wrapper {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 8px;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .email_header {
            background-color: #0070f3;
            padding: 30px;
            text-align: center;
            color: #ffffff;
        }

        .email_body {
            padding: 30px;
        }

        .email_footer {
            background-color: #f0f0f0;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #888;
        }

        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 12px 30px;
            background-color: #0070f3;
            color: #ffffff;
            text-align: center;
            border-radius: 5px;
            font-weight: bold;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 16px;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="email_wrapper">
        <div class="email_header">
            <h1>Account Activated</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="email_body">
            <p>Hello <%= user.name %>,</p>
            <p>We're excited to inform you that your account with EduConnextX has been successfully activated!</p>
            <p>You can now log in to your account and start exploring our services.</p>
            <p>If you have any questions or need assistance, feel free to reach out to us.</p>
            <p>Thank you for being a part of the EduConnextX community!</p>
        </div>
        <div class="email_footer">
            <p>If you need help, contact our support team at <a
                href="mailto:fedsi.yasser@gmail.com">support@ecx.com</a>.
            </p>
            <p>&copy; 2024 EduConnextX. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>